---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Shiba Inu Tools & Calculators | Life with Yukki"
  description="Free tools for Shiba Inu owners: puppy growth chart, weight tracker, cost calculator, and more. Track your Shiba's development."
  alternateUrls={{ en: '/tools/', ru: '/ru/instrumenty/' }}
>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Shiba Inu Tools</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Helpful calculators and trackers for Shiba Inu owners</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tools-grid">
        <a href="/tools/shiba-inu-puppy-growth-chart" class="tool-card card">
          <div class="tool-icon">üìä</div>
          <h2>Puppy Growth Chart</h2>
          <p>Track your Shiba Inu puppy's weight and compare it to breed averages. See if your pup is growing on track.</p>
          <div class="tool-features">
            <span class="feature">Weight tracking</span>
            <span class="feature">Age comparison</span>
            <span class="feature">Growth milestones</span>
          </div>
          <span class="btn">Open Tool</span>
        </a>

        <div class="tool-card card coming-soon">
          <div class="tool-icon">üí∞</div>
          <h2>Ownership Cost Calculator</h2>
          <p>Estimate the monthly and yearly costs of owning a Shiba Inu, including food, vet care, grooming, and supplies.</p>
          <div class="tool-features">
            <span class="feature">Monthly costs</span>
            <span class="feature">Yearly breakdown</span>
            <span class="feature">Lifetime estimate</span>
          </div>
          <span class="btn btn-disabled">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card card coming-soon">
          <div class="tool-icon">üçñ</div>
          <h2>Feeding Calculator</h2>
          <p>Calculate how much food your Shiba Inu needs based on age, weight, and activity level.</p>
          <div class="tool-features">
            <span class="feature">Portion sizes</span>
            <span class="feature">Calorie needs</span>
            <span class="feature">Feeding schedule</span>
          </div>
          <span class="btn btn-disabled">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .page-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .page-subtitle {
      font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
      color: var(--color-text-light);
    }

    .tools-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .tool-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    a.tool-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    }

    .tool-card.coming-soon {
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .tool-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .tool-card h2 {
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .tool-card p {
      color: var(--color-text-light);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .tool-features {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .feature {
      background-color: var(--color-secondary);
      color: var(--color-text);
      padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    }

    .btn-disabled {
      background-color: var(--color-text-light);
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .btn-disabled:hover {
      background-color: var(--color-text-light);
      transform: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .tools-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
